.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-RECEIVABLE-BALANCE-VARIANCE 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-receivable-balance-variance \- variance of receivable balances across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning channel-receivable-balance-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of receivable balances in millisatoshis across all peer channels.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key receivable_balance_variance_msat.
